quran[7{c,v,t}:
57,12,jis din tum momin mardon aur momin aurton ko dekho ge ke un ( ke imaan ) ka noor un ke agay agay aur dahni taraf chal raha hai ( to un se kaha jaye ga ke ) tum ko basharat ho ( ke aaj tumahray liye ) baagh hain jin ke taley nehrain beh rahi hain un mein hamesha raho ge. yahi barri kamyabi hai
57,13,uss din munhafiq mard aur munhafiq aurtain mominoun se kahin ge ke hamari taraf se ( shafqat ) kijiye ke hum bhi tumahray noor se roshni haasil karen. to un se kaha jaye ga ke peechay ko lout jao aur ( wahan ) noor talaash karo. phir un ke beech mein aik deewar khari kar di jaye gi. jis mein aik darwaaza hoga jo is ki janib androoni hai is mein to rehmat hai aur jo janib bairooni hai is taraf azaab ( o azziyat )
57,14,to munhafiq log mominoun se kahin ge kekiya hum ( duniya mein ) tumahray sath nah they woh kahin ge kyun nahi they. lekin tum ne khud apne tain bulaa mein dala aur ( hamaray haq mein hawadis ke ) munhtazir rahay aur ( islam mein ) shakkiya aur ( laa-ta-il ) aarzouon ne tum ko dhoka diya yahan taq ke khuda ka hukum aa pouncha aur khuda ke baray mein tum ko ( shetan ) daga baaz dagha deta raha
57,15,to aaj tum se muawza nahi liya jaye ga aur nah ( woh ) kafiroon hi se ( qubool kiya jaye ga ) tum sab ka thikana dozakh hai. ( ke ) wohi tumahray Laiq hai aur woh buri jagah hai
57,16,kiya abhi taq mominoun ke liye is ka waqt nahi aaya ke khuda ki yaad karne ke waqt aur ( quran ) jo ( khuday-e ) brhq ( ki taraf ) se nazil howa hai is ke suneney ke waqt un ke dil naram ho jaien aur woh un logon ki taraf nah ho jaien jin ko ( un se ) pehlay kitaaben di gayi theen. phir un par Zaman taweel guzar gaya to un ke dil sakht hogaye. aur un mein se aksar nafarman hain
57,17,jaan rakho ke khuda hi zameen ko is ke marnay ke baad zindah karta hai. hum ne apni nishanain tum se khol khol kar bayan kar di hain taakay tum samjhoo
57,18,jo log khairaat karne walay hain mard bhi aur aurtain bhi. aur khuda ko ( niyat ) naik ( aur khuloos se ) qarz dete hain un ko dochnd adakiya jaye ga aur un ke liye izzat ka sila hai
